sing a premium-based mechanism comparing the perpetual mark price to the underlying spot price. Funding payments occur every hour at minute zero, with rates typically ranging from -0.01% to +0.05% based on market sentiment. The decentralized nature means funding calculations are transparent and verifiable on-chain. Position holders pay or receive funding based on their side and the rate sign, with long positions paying when rates are positive."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
